snippet.title: Intellectual Wave
snippet.description:
Intellectual Wave's mission is to educate, to enlighten, and spread knowledge all around the globe through providing entertaining documentary-style videos. 

Every video take me about 80 to 100 hours of making, in order to complete. Even more if the video is longer. But i find a particular joy in making these videos and providing a educational value.

If you like our content, hit that subscribe button, and we wish from the depths of our hearts that these videos might help anyone who watches them, and gives them a better perspective in resolving the issues in their everyday life, and improve their lives to the better. 

𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐦 : @intellectualwave
𝐒𝐮𝐛𝐬𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐞  : https://www.youtube.com/IntellectualWave
